Metorex to Sell Interest in Sable Zinc Kabwe to Glencore

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-06-08T06:02:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/metorex-to-sell-its-stake-in-sable-zinc-kabwe-to-glencore-for-28-million.html
Metorex Ltd. (MTX)  said it has entered into
an agreement to sell its stake in Sable Zinc Kabwe Ltd. to
Glencore International Plc for about 190 million rand.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  